{
  "stem": "3605.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the money that my father-- and the valuable things that my father left me helped me to support myself, so I wasn't really a big burden on them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I even cooked something while they were all out at work, and I was there, illegal.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they even cleaned some of the toilets for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I shouldn't have to do that heavy, miserable job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the evening before, I had kind of a feeling that I am going to be caught.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So I took out those valuable things, and I said, here you have it-- whatever I had left.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "If you can help me with it, help me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "If not, you use it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It's going to be more handy for you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Where I would eventually go if I am caught, I won't need those things.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And, sure enough, they bribed two Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And that other woman, they bribed the people from the other woman, too-- together-- they put together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And those young men not only gave the money and the valuable things that I gave them, some of them gave even things that they had from their mothers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They were so anxious to-- to save me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And, sure enough, the two Germans took me out of the temple.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And there were open sewers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And we went into those sewers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they wanted my father's golden watch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I didn't leave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "This was the only thing I didn't want to part with, sentimentally.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And I gave them the golden watch, so I knew that they must have been bribed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And I went into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And, of course, I survived with a miracle again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Next morning, all the 500 people were taken to a forest nearby in Piotrkow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They were all shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
